My Story: Olympic gold medallist Rebecca Adlington on her swimming journey

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Olympic gold medallist Rebecca Adlington made a name for herself at the 2008 Beijing Olympics when she won two Gold medals in the 400m and the 800m freestyle.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
